title: KISS The Millenium Concert Mick E. Gee Remaster 2014
description:
This is another run Mick E. Gee took at making The Millenium cd sound as good as possible.
All the songs are sped up, but still in the same key/pitch as KISS performed the tracks.
EQ'd and tweaked a bunch of things so it sounded much warmer on the bottom end and less shrill on the top end. 
This is definately a way more enjoyable listen and easily improved the disc 100%.
